data.title: Tiger Shroff's 'heropanti' in debut film
data.meta_description: He is gutsy and he is adventurous. Newcomer Tiger Shroff showed off his daring side while filming "Heropanti", in which he insisted upon doing stunts himself.
data.text:
Ghai's new find Mishti on TV show

Actress Mishti, who has been launched by Subhash Ghai in Bollywood with "Kaanchi", will be seen on the small screen show "Ekk Nayi Pehchaan".

Soundarya honoured, mom 'proud'

Superstar Rajinikanth’s daughter Soundarya, whose directorial debut “Kochadaiiyaan” is set to release, was honoured with the NDTV Indian of the Year Technical Innovation in a Film award here Tuesday. And her mother Latha is relishing the moment.

Surrey's Simran Sidhu bags major role in Bollywood after winning reality show Bollywood Star

Simran Sidhu, resident of Surrey, has been named the winner of the OMNI reality competition show, Bollywood Star.
